egistration.'=>'Activa bloquear registro de administrador.','Enable Mask Login Errors.'=>'Activa la máscara de errores de acceso.','Display "All Options" menu item'=>'Mostrar el elemento de menú "Todas las opciones"','Display "Blocking" menu item'=>'Mostrar el elemento de menú "Bloqueos"','Display "Live Traffic" menu item'=>'Mostrar el elemento de menú "Tráfico en vivo"','/set-country-bypass/'=>'/establecer-pais-omitido/','Wordfence Security'=>'Wordfence Security','Wordfence'=>'Wordfence','Wordfence Security - Anti-virus, Firewall and Malware Scan'=>'Wordfence Security - Anti-virus, Firewall and Malware Scan','https://www.wordfence.com/help/dashboard/#dashboard-status'=>'https://www.wordfence.com/help/dashboard/#dashboard-status','https://www.wordfence.com/help/scan/#scan-status'=>'https://www.wordfence.com/help/scan/#scan-status','https://www.wordfence.com/help/firewall/#firewall-status'=>'https://www.wordfence.com/help/firewall/#firewall-status','Macao'=>'RAE de Macao (China)','Mongolia'=>'Mongolia','Myanmar'=>'Birmania','Mali'=>'Malí','Marshall Islands'=>'Islas Marshall','Madagascar'=>'Madagascar','Saint Martin'=>'San Martín','Montenegro'=>'Montenegro','Moldova, Republic of'=>'Moldavia','Monaco'=>'Mónaco','Morocco'=>'Marruecos','Libyan Arab Jamahiriya'=>'Libia','Latvia'=>'Letonia','Luxembourg'=>'Luxemburgo','Lithuania'=>'Lituania','Lesotho'=>'Lesoto','Liberia'=>'Liberia','Sri Lanka'=>'Sri Lanka','Liechtenstein'=>'Liechtenstein','Saint Lucia'=>'Santa Lucía','Lebanon'=>'Líbano','Lao Peoples Democratic Republic'=>'República democrática de los pueblos de Laos','Kazakhstan'=>'Kazajistán','Cayman Islands'=>'Islas Caimán','Kuwait'=>'Kuwait','South Korea'=>'Corea del Sur','North Korea'=>'Corea del Norte','Saint Kitts and Nevis'=>'San Cristóbal y Nieves','Comoros'=>'Comoras','Kiribati'=>'Kiribati','Cambodia'=>'Camboya','Kyrgyzstan'=>'Kirguistán','Kenya'=>'Kenia','Japan'=>'Japón','Jordan'=>'Jordania','Jamaica'=>'Jamaica','Jersey'=>'Jersey','Italy'=>'Italia','Iceland'=>'Isl